{"tid":825303,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日放假 想組義工團去清理街道","createTime":"2018-09-17T13:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T19:41:40.000Z","uid":4548,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"22ff830b58962b23ce751abc70a7745ed843149d","tid":825303,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"眼見樹木倒塌好嚴重，想盡一分綿力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人得閒又有興趣可以一齊去？ <br />\n邊區就未諗到，大家有冇建議邊到情況比較嚴峻同緊急 而市民又可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7b978d40df242f6638b667b2a18e2a21dc9e1c","tid":825303,"uid":30413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ff830b58962b23ce751abc70a7745ed843149d","tid":825303,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"眼見樹木倒塌好嚴重，想盡一分綿力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人得閒又有興趣可以一齊去？ <br />\n邊區就未諗到，大家有冇建議邊到情況比較嚴峻同緊急 而市民又可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，聽日要返工，幫你推下"},{"pid":"3b6166adac249d106e2ca6e5f0abb2d3d08a5618","tid":825303,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63cf3b012fad027f298df15b6fa108c389c3a12","tid":825303,"uid":4548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"🔊🔊🔊緊急召集義工‼️<br />\n<br />\n「山竹」過後，大量垃圾透過海水沖入杏花邨內。🌊<br />\n<br />\n為避免垃圾再次流入海中，現時大量義工在杏花邨協助清理垃圾，當中超過200公斤的膠樽已送到綠在東區協助回收<br />\n<br />\n但由於所有膠樽曾經與其他泥石一同捲在海浪中，未清洗過，加上未除樽蓋及分類，回收商拒絕回收🙅&zwj;♂️。<br />\n<br />\n🆘因此在此緊急召集各路義工協助，將杏花邨義工辛苦救回的塑膠樽，可以真正進行回收再造♻️<br />\n<br />\n日期︰9月18日至9月21日<br />\n時間︰早上9時至6時<br />\n地點︰綠在東區<br />\n協助內容︰除蓋、簡單清洗、分類<br />\n查詢﹕27782330<br />\n<br />\n不分時段，即使只有部份時間可以幫手都冇問題，希望救得一個得一個。💪💪<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2D4wtCc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2D4wtCc&d=8xrTX4oEgcXVd4BAtBD8ADCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c5b6e523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2D4wtCc</a><br />\n<br />\n綠在東區：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Dg2B63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Dg2B63&d=8xrTX4oEgcXVd4BAtBD8ADCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5d21cfc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Dg2B63</a><br />\n<br />\n#義工 #做義工 #香港義工 #義工招募 #招募義工 #義工情報 #義工情報局 #義工資訊 #義工活動 #義工配對 #義工服務 #義工宣傳 #義工介紹 #義工轉介<br />\n<br />\n啱啱搵到呢個都幾好 有興趣都可以去幫手！"},{"pid":"8c7765d2daea9a66b6ef93c1d7612823cc04bc9f","tid":825303,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"星期六日仲要唔要人"},{"pid":"eec896933d5254c5cfeb309bd23cbe768ecbd756","tid":825303,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c7765d2daea9a66b6ef93c1d7612823cc04bc9f","tid":825303,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"星期六日仲要唔要人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"我聽日去做 再幫你問下。 聽日覆返你"},{"pid":"1c81b498f538575d7e3fa5daec18f303e85cff1b","tid":825303,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"食德好 Food Grace<br />\n<br />\n【📢📢緊急義工招募: 颱風後飯盒處理🙏🙏】<br />\n<br />\n山竹遠離香港，各區道路還未清理好🚷食德好已忙處理颱風後的學童飯盒 💪明早，我們急需義工，協助我們處理超過8萬個飯盒接收和派贈工作。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣相助的義工，請pm我們，告知您們可幫忙的地區，請同時提供聯絡電話，以便聯繫！每區需要6-10名義工 🙏<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2018年9月18日<br />\n時間: 上午9時-下午3時 (只幫忙上午或下午亦可)<br />\n地區: A/葵涌區 B/沙田石門 C/柴灣 D/油塘 E/元朗"},{"pid":"2c832a1263bdd0a98aa26aac582d8bf603c361a7","tid":825303,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c81b498f538575d7e3fa5daec18f303e85cff1b","tid":825303,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit